---
title: Lemony Chicken & Zucchini Rice Bowls with Chicken Thighs & Garlic Crema
description: Thanks to our pre-marinated chicken thighs, you'll have an ultra-flavorful, extra-lemony chicken and rice bowl on the table in a quick 20 minutes. Sizzle up a skillet of zucchini, red onion, scallions, and chicken, then serve it over a bowl of lemony rice. A drizzle of tangy, zippy garlic crema—plus an extra squeeze of lemon—brings it home.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/677d613ea90519950138cdc6-2f7bb027.jpeg
